Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
On behalf of our client, we are pleased to present an exciting leasing opportunity
at POINT WEST PLACE in Framingham, Massachusetts. Located at 111 Speen Street,
POINT WEST PLACE is a distinctive five-story, 115,000 SF building located off the Mass Pike at Exit 13. The institutional ownership has recently completed an extensive common area and amenity renovation, including an upgraded fitness center and expanded café seating area. The building features an on-site cafeteria, fitness center, on-site management, basement storage area, 4.0/1,000 SF parking ratio and covered parking.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A Office Space at 111 Speen Street, Framingham
